{"tid":2513961,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店請人","createTime":"2021-05-03T02:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T03:56:23.000Z","uid":397359,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0eff6de758be8031f76b7855eee5fd332981afd6","tid":2513961,"uid":397359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"天水圍區米線<br />\n想請一名水吧同廚房<br />\n廚房起薪16k-18k(視乎熟手程度而定),每日10個鐘,45分鐘食飯時間,每個月4日day off,mpf,因為太忙勞工假可能會放唔足,會同你傾補水<br />\n水吧起薪12k-14k(視乎熟手程度而定),其他同上<br />\n廚房唔介意你唔識煮,我地會教,但最少你要有1-2年廚房經驗<br />\n水吧一樣,都係要有一兩年經驗<br />\n另招招聘樓面part time 60/hr<br />\n利申真係好忙,想hea住做既真係唔好搞我地,可能會有人話出手低,但我地都係小店,唔係人地D咩大公司,個價錢比起區內甚至高少少<br />\n唔介意你係咩背景,只要係手足我就一定請<br />\n有興趣既留低TG,會有專人回覆你(即係我)"},{"pid":"d3b2216c6ee5fd6ba6a2968ca7dc975b29c5701a","tid":2513961,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:07:39.000Z","msg":"冇30k/ month 又唔可以聚賭 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede5e4654df5cf0a5e0770f4e66fc71a1ad6ee5a","tid":2513961,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"Btw 麗江？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10070dd123b4cee704c2efff02e937f19a1e6856","tid":2513961,"uid":397359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b2216c6ee5fd6ba6a2968ca7dc975b29c5701a","tid":2513961,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:07:39.000Z","msg":"冇30k/ month 又唔可以聚賭 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"邊個話唔可以聚賭,乜都有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a83599b364f305719d81a1f7dee6fd6f5d7f512","tid":2513961,"uid":238696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:14:20.000Z","msg":"講到份工咁忙，但係食飯連一個鐘都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=